 motion models, which are demonstrating the potential for more intuitive and responsive human-AI interactions.\n===Voice Arena===\n<title>[2502.19053] Blending Optimal Control and Biologically Plausible Learning for Noise-Robust Physical Neural Networks</title>", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false}}
